</div1>


<div1 xml:lang="en" type="translation">
                
                <pb facs="20160613_140738.jpg"/>
                
                <ab>
                    French Sudan
                </ab>
                
                <ab>
                    Major State
                </ab>
                
                <ab>
                    Perpignan April 4th 1894
                </ab>
                
                <ab>
                    Lieutenant Berge to Mister
                    Minister of the Colonies.
                </ab>
                
                <p>
                    Mister Minister,
                    
                    I have the honor to give you a report
                    that in compliance with the Instructions of
                    Mister Governor of French
                    Sudan I will render myself in Paris before
                    the end of this week and put myself
                    at your disposition for the information that
                    you would have to demand from me on the border
                    regions of the coast of Liberia.
                </p>
                
                <p>
                    The reasons of material order put me
                    in the impossibility of rendering myself 
                    earlier in Paris.
                    H. Berge
                </p>
                
                <ab>
                    POLITCAL OFFICE
                    APR 9 94 <!-- This section is stamped -->
                </ab>
                
